ed-in-west-bank-shooting-attack-israeli-army-searching-for-assailant/0000018e-8435-df27-adee-a6ff9fc90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯谈判陷入停滞可能会将与真主党的冲突转变为全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/the-northern-front-heats-back-up-and-israel-readies-for-larger-war-with-hezbollah/0000018e-81a8-d4d2-abfe-a3e9c5630000</link><description>经过数周的相对平静后，北部的紧张局势再次升温，以色列和真主党相互攻击并造成人员伤亡。 ■ 在政治方面，以色列议会准备就征兵豁免问题展开斗争，内塔尼亚胡继续与拜登进行小规模战争，这次“向哈马斯发送消息”</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 04:00:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article/.premium/the-northern-front-heats-back-up-and-israel-readies-for-larger-war-with-hezbollah/0000018e-81a8-d4d2-abfe-a3e9c5630000</guid></item><item><title>被绑架以色列士兵的父母：国家吓到了我们。我们保持沉默——直到今天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-live/hezbollah-operatives-among-eight-people-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon/0000018e-829d-d4d2-abfe-a3dd0c720000</link><description>约旦河西岸枪击事件造成三人受伤；以色列军队搜寻袭击者 ■ 真主党特工在以色列对黎巴嫩的袭击中丧生 8 人死亡 ■ 以色列国防军在 Al-Shifa 医院开展行动，称有 200 名恐怖分子被打死 ■ 哈马斯发布了军事部门负责人穆罕默德·戴夫的录音，呼吁阿拉伯世界“向巴勒斯坦进军” ” ■ 白宫表示正在努力重新安排已取消的与以色列代表团有关拉法选项的会议</description><pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 01:18:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-28/ty-article-live/hezbollah-operatives-among-eight-people-killed-in-israeli-strike-in-lebanon/0000018e-829d-d4d2-abfe-a3dd0c720000</guid></item><item><title>以色列司法监察员称高等法院法官卡布行为不道德</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-judiciary-ombudsman-says-high-court-justice-kabub-acted-unethically/0000018e-816f-df27-adee-a7ff198c0000</link><description>监察员裁定，查立德·卡布 (Chaled Kabub) 法官未经授权接受媒体采访，违反了法官道德准则，并驳回了卡布 (Kabub) 对他参与涉及其子女的法律纠纷审判的指控的回应。所有针对他的投诉都是由右翼活动家谢伊·格利克（Shay Glick）提交的</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:20:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israels-judiciary-ombudsman-says-high-court-justice-kabub-acted-unethically/0000018e-816f-df27-adee-a7ff198c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡政府准备招募极端正统派入伍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</link><description>提交请求的截止日期已于周三午夜到期。如果不提交，内阁关于免除极端正统派男子征兵的决定将于周一到期，他们将被征召服兵役</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 20:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-ag-opposes-netanyahu-govts-attempt-to-extend-deadline-on-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-816c-df27-adee-a7feb2b10000</guid></item><item><title>正统派兵役豁免危机对以色列政治来说是一个地震事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</link><description>即使本杰明·内塔尼亚胡未能通过一项免除所有犹太学院学生服兵役的法律，极端正统派政党也可能会留在政府，但在下一次选举后，他们可能会长期处于反对派状态</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:56:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/the-haredi-exemptions-law-crisis-will-draw-israels-political-lines-for-a-generation/0000018e-815b-ddea-a1de-835f4b900000</guid></item><item><title>“压迫越多，以色列的年轻阿拉伯人就越强调他们的巴勒斯坦身份”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 19:23:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-03-27/ty-article-podcast/the-more-oppression-there-is-the-more-younger-arabs-in-israel-identify-as-palestinians/0000018e-8071-d861-adff-ce7d3b6b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列士兵在加沙南部战斗中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-n