protest/0000018e-80a5-d5aa-abdf-f9bf188b0000</link><description>警方在房间里捣毁后没有找到他们要找的东西，但最终逮捕了这名活动人士，并试图将她拘留五天。 “我们作为激进主义的行动空间正在缩小，”她说</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:19:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/police-ransack-bedroom-of-israeli-who-participated-in-anti-govt-protest/0000018e-80a5-d5aa-abdf-f9bf188b0000</guid></item><item><title>白宫：内塔尼亚胡决定“重新安排”以色列代表团赴美参与拉法行动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-he-pulled-israels-delegation-to-u-s-to-send-a-message-to-hamas/0000018e-8084-d49b-a3bf-f49f81230000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡似乎推翻了之前的声明，即在美国决定不否决联合国安理会停火决议后，他将以色列代表团撤回华盛顿，以此向哈马斯发出“信息”，即它不能依赖国际压力</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 16:09:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-says-he-pulled-israels-delegation-to-u-s-to-send-a-message-to-hamas/0000018e-8084-d49b-a3bf-f49f81230000</guid></item><item><title>以色列裔美国经济学家、诺贝尔奖获得者丹尼尔·卡尼曼去世，享年 90 岁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-american-economist-and-nobel-laureate-daniel-kahneman-dies-at-90/0000018e-8094-d113-a1ce-9a97ccc10000</link><description>卡尼曼与阿莫斯·特沃斯基联合开展的将心理学见解融入经济学的开创性工作为他赢得了 2002 年诺贝尔奖。他是内塔尼亚胡政府司法改革的直言不讳的批评者</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:47:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/israeli-american-economist-and-nobel-laureate-daniel-kahneman-dies-at-90/0000018e-8094-d113-a1ce-9a97ccc10000</guid></item><item><title>被停职的以色列政府发言人埃隆·利维正式被解雇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/suspended-israeli-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-officially-dismissed/0000018e-803d-de8e-adae-acfd6d5f0000</link><description>在与英国外交部长发生推特争议后，一名政府官员表示，利维“偏离了以色列的信息，采取了太多自由”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:13:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/suspended-israeli-government-spokesman-eylon-levy-officially-dismissed/0000018e-803d-de8e-adae-acfd6d5f0000</guid></item><item><title>在加沙受伤的以色列歌手拒绝点燃独立日火炬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-singer-wounded-in-gaza-refuses-to-light-ceremonial-independence-day-torch/0000018e-8000-dc05-abef-abc9de140000</link><description>演员、歌手兼以色列国防军预备役军人伊丹·阿梅迪拒绝了这一请求，称其他人比他更值得，他希望“由于我写下的文字，而不是由于战争英雄主义，他将被授予点燃火炬的功绩”</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 15:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-singer-wounded-in-gaza-refuses-to-light-ceremonial-independence-day-torch/0000018e-8000-dc05-abef-abc9de140000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡预计将请求以色列高等法院延长哈雷迪法案草案的期限</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-expected-to-ask-israels-high-court-for-extension-over-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-7fe3-d669-a9fe-7fef35dc0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡向其联盟中的极端正统党领导人保证，政府对犹太学校的资助不会受到影响，因为这是一项可以免除所有正统派男子应征入伍的法案谈判的一部分。然而，目前尚不清楚总理如何证明这一点</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 14:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-expected-to-ask-israels-high-court-for-extension-over-haredi-draft-bill/0000018e-7fe3-d669-a9fe-7fef35dc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩造成七人死亡后，以色列人在以色列北部发射的重型火箭弹中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-in-rocket-barrage-fired-at-northern-israel-after-idf-strikes-in-lebanon/0000018e-7eed-d9f5-a7ae-7eedc2f60000</link><description>来自以色列北部德鲁兹村庄的扎赫尔·比沙拉 (Zaher Bishara) 在真主党向什莫纳镇发射约 30 枚火箭弹后在一栋工业建筑中身亡。此次袭击是对以色列对黎巴嫩发动袭击的报复，该袭击造成七人死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:47:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article/.premium/israeli-killed-in-rocket-barrage-fired-at-northern-israel-after-idf-strikes-in-lebanon/0000018e-7eed-d9f5-a7ae-7eedc2f60000</guid></item><item><title>解释：谁是犹太极端正统派亲巴勒斯坦活动家 Neturei Karta</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-neturei-karta-the-jewish-ultra-orthodox-pro-palestinian-activists/0000018e-7039-df85-afde-f77d40640000</link><description>在网上和街头，这些激烈反犹太复国主义的极端正统犹太活动分子对他们完全回归《托拉法》的独裁目标以及对哈马斯、伊朗和真主党的拥抱保持沉默。目前，他们的“停止加沙迫害”信息在美国进步示威活动中受到热烈欢迎</description><pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 13:18:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-27/ty-article-magazine/.premium/explained-who-are-neturei-karta-the-jewish-ultra-orthodox-pro-palestinian-activists/0000018e-7039-df85-afde-f77d40640000</guid></item></channel></rss>